phase2.explanation:
You're trying to use a Tilemap that was never assigned.

**The fix:**
```csharp
void Start()
{
    if (tilemap == null)
    {
        tilemap = GetComponent<Tilemap>();
    }

    if (tilemap != null)
    {
        tilemap.SetTile(new Vector3Int(0, 0, 0), tile);
    }
}
```

**Sharp-chan says:**
"Always check if tilemap is assigned before using it."
